OL,3,CRetired engineer found guilty of Ulez
OL,4,Ccamera explosion
OL,6,FA man who "strongly opposed" the ultra-
OL,7,Flow emission zone scheme has been
OL,8,Ffound guilty of causing an explosion
OL,9,Flikely to endanger life, after he blew
OL,10,Fup a Ulez camera in south-east London.
OL,12,FWatch the moment the camera exploded
OL,13,Fbelow:
OL,15,FKevin Rees, a retired electrical
OL,16,Fappliances engineer, caused damage to
OL,17,Fproperty, cars and a child's bedroom
OL,18,Fwith his 'homemade bomb'- a 'low-
OL,19,Fsophistication improvised explosive
OL,20,Fdevice' (IED) in December 2023.
