OL,3,CRetired engineer found guilty of Ulez
OL,4,Ccamera explosion
OL,6,FThe court heard that he planted the
OL,7,Fdevice near the camera, before
OL,8,Flighting a fuse and quickly walking
OL,9,Faway.
OL,11,FDuring the trial, Rees agreed with
OL,12,Fprosecutor Simon Denison KC that, at
OL,13,Fthe time of the incident, he "strongly
OL,14,Fopposed" the Ulez scheme ` and the
OL,15,FMayor of London, Sadiq Khan.
OL,17,F"I dislike him, dislike what he has
OL,18,Fdone to London," the defendant said.
