OL,6,FDetectives found that Rees had posted
OL,7,Fmultiple times about Ulez cameras and
OL,8,Fencouraging others to damage them.
OL,10,FDetective Superintendent James Derham,
OL,11,Fwho leads local policing in the Bexley
OL,12,Farea, said:
OL,14,F"It was miraculous that nobody was
OL,15,Fkilled or seriously injured in the
OL,16,Flarge explosion caused by Rees.
