OL,3,CRetired engineer found guilty of Ulez
OL,4,Ccamera explosion
OL,6,F"He showed a complete disregard for
OL,7,Fthe welfare and safety of the people
OL,8,Fwho live in, or were travelling
OL,9,Fthrough, the area at the time of the
OL,10,Fexplosion ` all because he was unhappy
OL,11,Fwith the Ulez scheme."
OL,13,FCameras have been repeatedly damaged
OL,14,Fafter the Ulez area was expanded to
OL,15,Fcover all of London in 2023.
OL,17,FThe camera that Rees exploded had been
OL,18,Finstalled earlier that day, but in an
OL,19,Funrelated incident was cut down by
OL,20,Fsomebody else.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
