OL,6,FBethan David, the head of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service's counter
OL,8,Fterrorism division said that Rees'
OL,9,Factions were not "an act of protest or
OL,10,Fmomentary vandalism".
OL,12,FInstead, she said that:
OL,14,F"This was a deliberate and dangerous
OL,15,Fattack involving a home-made explosive
OL,16,Fdevice, carried out in a residential
OL,17,Fstreet and designed to destroy public
OL,18,Finfrastructure.
