OL,3,CRetired engineer found guilty of Ulez
OL,4,Ccamera explosion
OL,6,F"Kevin Rees knowingly and
OL,7,Fintentionally placed an explosive
OL,8,Fdevice next to the Ulez camera, lit
OL,9,Fthe fuse and retreated before the
OL,10,Fexplosion, showing clear planning and
OL,11,Fan obvious disregard for the safety of
OL,12,Fothers.
OL,14,F"Whatever his views on the Ulez
OL,15,Fscheme, Kevin Rees crossed a serious
OL,16,Fline by constructing a home-made bomb
OL,17,Fand detonating it in a public place.
OL,18,FIt was pure chance that no-one
OL,19,Fsuffered serious injury or worse."
